M||tx|---
M||titl|Avoid Duplicate Serialization in RSC Props
M||impa|lo
M||impa|reduces network payload by avoiding duplicate serialization
M||tags|server, rsc, serialization, props, client-cp
M||tx|---
M|Avoi|**Im|lo (reduces network payload by avoiding duplicate serialization)**
M|Avoi|tx|RSC→client serialization deduplicates by object reference, not value. Same reference = serialized once; new reference = serialized again. Do transformations (`.toSorted()`, `.filter()`, `.map()`) in client, not server.
M|Avoi|**In|**
M|Avoi|tx|```tsx
M|Avoi|// R|sends 6 strings (2 arrays × 3 items)
M|Avoi|tx|<ClientList usernames={usernames} usernamesOrdered={usernames.toSorted()} />
M|Avoi|tx|```
M|Avoi|**Co|**
M|Avoi|tx|```tsx
M|Avoi|// R|send once
M|Avoi|tx|<ClientList usernames={usernames} />
M|Avoi|// C|transform there
M|Avoi|tx|'use client'
M|Avoi|tx|const sorted = useMemo(() => [...usernames].sort(), [usernames])
M|Avoi|tx|```
M|Avoi|**Ne|**
M|Avoi|Dedu|
M|Avoi|- `s|**hi impact** - array + all primitives fully duplicated
M|Avoi|- `o|**lo impact** - array duplicated, but nested objects deduplicated by reference
M|Avoi|tx|```tsx
M|Avoi|tx|// string[] - duplicates everything
M|Avoi|tx|usernames={['a','b']} sorted={usernames.toSorted()} // sends 4 strings
M|Avoi|tx|// object[] - duplicates array structure only
M|Avoi|user|1},{id:2}]} sorted={us.toSorted()} // sends 2 arrays + 2 unique objects (not 4)
M|Avoi|tx|```
M|Avoi|**Op|**
M|Avoi|- Ar|`.toSorted()`, `.filter()`, `.map()`, `.slice()`, `[...arr]`
M|Avoi|- Ob|`{...obj}`, `Object.assign()`, `structuredClone()`, `JSON.parse(JSON.stringify())`
M|Avoi|**Mo|**
M|Avoi|tx|```tsx
M|Avoi|tx|// ❌ Bad
M|Avoi|tx|<C us={us} active={us.filter(u => u.active)} />
M|Avoi|tx|<C pd={pd} productName={pd.name} />
M|Avoi|tx|// ✅ Good
M|Avoi|tx|<C us={us} />
M|Avoi|tx|<C pd={pd} />
M|Avoi|tx|// Do filtering/destructuring in client
M|Avoi|tx|```
M|Avoi|**Ex|** Pass derived data when transformation is expensive or client doesn't need original.